claim.claim-text:
1. An apparatus comprising: 
a first chamber containing a first composition, the first composition comprising a first active ingredient effective in treating acne; 
a second chamber containing a second composition comprising a second active ingredient that is incompatible with the first active ingredient; 
pump means for moving the first and second compositions out of the first and second chambers, respectively; and 
one or more outlets for dispensing the first and second compositions.

20. An apparatus as in claim 1 wherein the second composition comprises 
(i) a polar solvent; 
(ii) a thickening agent selected from the group consisting of acrylic acid polymers, polyacrylamides and combinations thereof; 
(iii) benzoyl peroxide; 
(iv) alkyl benzoate; and optionally 
(v) a synthetic cleanser.

21. An apparatus comprising: 
a first chamber containing a first composition, the first composition comprising an effective acne-treating amount of an antibiotic; 
a second chamber containing a second composition comprising an active ingredient that is incompatible with the antibiotic; 
pump means for moving the first and second compositions out of the first and second chambers; and 
one or more outlets for dispensing the first and second compositions.

26. An apparatus comprising: 
a first chamber containing a first composition, the first composition comprising an effective acne-treating amount of benzoyl peroxide; 
a second chamber containing a second composition comprising an active ingredient that is incompatible with benzoyl peroxide; 
pump means for moving the first and second compositions out of the first and second chambers; and 
one or more outlets for dispensing the first and second compositions.

31. An apparatus comprising: 
a first chamber containing a first composition, the first composition comprising a retinoid; 
a second chamber containing a second composition comprising an active ingredient that is incompatible with the retinoid; 
pump means for moving the first and second compositions out of the first and second chambers; and 
one or more outlets for dispensing the first and second compositions.
